Responsibility
· Partner with business stakeholder to identify hiring needs and build up consistent talent pool from short-term and long-term strategies
· Lead end-to-end recruitment across many businesses teams by working closely with business/managers.
· Develop and manage recruitment channels and make the channel efficiency analysis and reporting.
· Manage both online and offline recruitment solutions in employer branding and engagement.
· Support various HR initiatives and projects.
· Identify and source high quality candidates through various channels. Continuously explores new recruiting sources, job boards, and forums and social networking site.
· Employee Engagement -- Initiates and implements action plans in collaboration with management to retain and grow our talent that results in a high engagement and high-performance culture.
· Monitor HR policies, practices and processes to determine efficiency and effectiveness. Recommends improvements to achieve and deliver improved results.
· Manage recruitment database, ensure that it is up-to-date and generate reports on a regular basis for the team and business. Provide regular market information and insight to internal team and business stakeholder regarding the talent trend and etc.; 
Requirement
？· Bachelor degree or above, at least 8 years HR professional working experience;
· Quick learner with the ability to handle a variety of tasks;
· Excellent command of both written and spoken English;
· Independent, creative and with a strong sense of responsibility;
· Accountable, open minded and sense of innovation; Able to work in the pressure and result-driven;

岗位职责：
1、	根据公司战略与业务规划，分析各部门招聘需求，编制人员招聘计划并组织实施，协助HRD完善招聘体系;
2、	负责海外公司筹备工作，协助海外子公司人力资源管理体系建设；
3、全面参与各岗位的招聘运作，包括人才搜寻、面试和评估、与业务部门协调、促成招聘决定、录用商谈、确保顺利入职;
4、从招聘的角度与业务部门紧密配合，针对各职位的进展提供高效的招聘建议与面试流程辅导;
5、招聘数据分析，渠道诊断，市场动态调研，及时调整用人方案，拓展探寻更多招聘渠道;
6、带领招聘团队，满足公司发展对人员招聘的需求，对招聘效果进行分析、评估，制定改进措施。
任职要求:
1、本科及以上学历，英语流利；人力资源、管理学专业；至少五年以上汽车行业招聘工作经验，其中有人事团队管理经验三年以上；有外资企业工作经验优先；
2、具备高度敬业精神及工作激情，能接受高强度的工作，工作态度积极乐观；
3、熟悉长期激励及短期激励政策及方式，有丰富的海外合规处理经验；
4、熟悉海外企业的招聘流程及各种招聘渠道，有猎聘经验者优先考虑；
5、有一定学习力、执行力和自驱力；有良好的团队合作意识。

